    _ â‰¤ â€–bs.basis.proj mâ€– * â€–sum_nâ€– := ContinuousLinearMap.le_opNorm _ _
    _ â‰¤ bs.basicSequenceConstant * â€–âˆ‘ i âˆˆ Finset.range n, a i â€¢ bs iâ€– :=
